{"tid":1234044,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"(集思廣益） 夠鐘啦，參觀禮賓府定機場？","createTime":"2019-06-17T00:17:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T00:35:58.000Z","uid":253438,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e94074c84365495c43325a75ccd919dfd8056850","tid":1234044,"uid":253438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T00:17:47.000Z","msg":"追post 追到成晚冇瞓過，<br />\n睇咗兩個post覺得都係幾好嘅選擇，，<br />\n大家覺得發夢去邊好？<br />\n我知有人投票去狗屋，<br />\n但覺得無法達到目的兼且自投羅網。<br />\n<br />\n禮賓府可以脅迫目標人物，<br />\n冇得比佢又玩鳩香港人。<br />\n<br />\n機場可以大規模影響港聲譽，<br />\n強迫正視，<br />\n亦相對對人安全，<br />\n但人數一定要多，<br />\n如果唔係變小學雞參觀機場。<br />\n<br />\n禮賓府正皮<br />\n機場負皮<br />\n<br />\n利申：同夢境有關而已<br />\n<br />\n請參考相關post：<br />\n<br />\n［兵法］我地慢慢失去主導權，再咁落去會輸<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1233658\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1233658</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n係咪應該開始諗下一步<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1233825\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1233825</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4731a784e0325c5bcb96e69a9c9cf6249f44791b","tid":1234044,"uid":253438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T00:20:35.000Z","msg":"大家好，我係林鄭，我依家胸有成竹，可以講贏硬你地！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1233828\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1233828</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ace05814852f568a174f1b592a5a19929aa3d6c4","tid":1234044,"uid":253438,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T00:22:00.000Z","msg":"如果發夢淨係去返龍和添美<br />\n真係重蹈覆轍only"},{"pid":"d29abe1cecb94b6278e4c7c5047abb2168eaeca0","tid":1234044,"uid":253438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T00:23:59.000Z","msg":"Push myself"},{"pid":"b9df74b3b484e06236a19f20d46f65d0ee893e5a","tid":1234044,"uid":253438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T00:24:43.000Z","msg":"推多一野"},{"pid":"e2e6ca5afa096e14ce4812920490a3a363d909aa","tid":1234044,"uid":199120,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"c